data.title: Heilbronn, Baden-Württemberg, Germany
data.text:
Heilbronn, a city in Baden-Württemberg, Germany, is located on the Neckar River, 50 km north of Stuttgart. Its history dates back to the 1st century AD, and it has a rich heritage, including medieval architecture, a thriving wine industry, and a vibrant arts and culture scene. The city experiences a temperate climate with warm summers and mild winters.
